A gefe daya kuma, hukumar kwallon kafa ta kudancin Amurka ta ce, an daga gasar Copa America ta wannan shekarar zuwa shekara mai zuwa daga 12 ga watan Yuni zuwa 12 ga watan Yulin 2021.
