Shin barkewar wannan cuta zai taimakawa yunkurin da akeyi na haramta cin naman dabbobin dawa a duniya da kuma kare lafiyar jama'a ?.
Masana na da ra'ayin cewa kalubale ne babba, amma ba abu ne da za'a ce bazai iya faruwa ba.
Kwayoyin cutar da ke haifar da mummunar cutar na numfashi (SARS) da kuma Tsakiyar Tsakiyar Tsakiyar Yan Sanda (MERS) an kuma yi imanin sun samo asali ne daga jemagu amma sun tsalle cikin mutane ta hanyar kuliyoyin rakakai da raƙuma bi da bi, a cewar jami'an na WHO.
